trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> class modifies the distinguished name of an object.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> modifica o nome diferenciado de um objeto.

trans-unit.source: This class moves an object to a new parent and/or renames the object.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe move um objeto para um novo pai e/ou renomeia o objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.#ctor" /> cria uma instância do objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.#ctor" /> cria uma instância do objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: The current distinguished name of the object.
trans-unit.target: O nome diferenciado atual do objeto.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the new parent of the object.
trans-unit.target: O nome diferenciado do novo pai do objeto.

trans-unit.source: The new distinguished name of the object.
trans-unit.target: O novo nome diferenciado do objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String,System.String)" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> object using the specified object name, parent name, and new object name.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String,System.String)" /> cria uma instância do objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> usando o nome de objeto especificado, o nome do pai e o nome do novo objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.DeleteOldRdn" /> property specifies whether to delete the old relative distinguished name (RDN) of the object.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.DeleteOldRdn" /> especifica se é preciso excluir o antigo RDN (nome diferenciado relativo) do objeto.

trans-unit.source: This property is <see langword="true" /> if the RDN should be deleted or <see langword="false" /> if it should not be deleted.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é <see langword="true" /> se o RDN deve ser excluído ou <see langword="false" /> se ele não deve ser excluído.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.DistinguishedName" /> property contains the distinguished name of the object.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.DistinguishedName" /> contém o nome diferenciado do objeto.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the object.
The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.NewName" /> property contains the new object name.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.NewName" /> contém o nome do novo objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.NewParentDistinguishedName" /> property contains the distinguished name of the new parent of the object.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.NewParentDistinguishedName" /> contém o nome diferenciado do novo pai do objeto.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the new parent of the object.
trans-unit.target: O nome diferenciado do novo pai do objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.ToXmlNode(System.Xml.XmlDocument)" /> method creates an XML node from the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest.ToXmlNode(System.Xml.XmlDocument)" /> cria um nó XML com base no objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> especificado.
O tipo do objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> resultante.
